Privacy Policy
At Kenzi Tracker, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our application.
1. Information We Collect
We may collect personal information from you when you use Kenzi Tracker, including but not limited to:
Username and password for authentication.
Event or class details, including attendance data and QR code scans.
Usage data, such as the features you access and your interactions with the app.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to provide and improve Kenzi Tracker, including:
Authenticating your account and providing access to your events or classes.
Tracking attendance through scanned QR codes and ensuring data accuracy.
Improving app functionality and user experience.
3. Data Storage and Security
Kenzi Tracker stores attendance and QR code data locally on your device. This data is encrypted and only accessible to you and authorized systems. We implement security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or modification.
4. Sharing Your Information
We do not share your personal information with third parties, except when required by law or when you provide explicit consent. We may share anonymized usage data with third parties to help us improve the app.
5. Data Retention
We will retain your information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. If you wish to delete your account or request that we no longer use your information, you can contact us at
connect@kenzi.ai
.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us at
connect@kenzi.ai
.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make changes, we will notify you by updating the policy on this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
8. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
connect@kenzi.ai
.